OL,6,FJersey Police Chief Officer, Robin
OL,7,FSmith, says: "These operations are
OL,8,Fmasquerading as legitimate banking
OL,9,Finstitutions, utilising clever social
OL,10,Fengineering techniques to inject a
OL,11,Fsense of urgency and financial
OL,12,Fjeopardy whilst also offering an
OL,13,Fentirely false, professional calm and
OL,14,Freassuring tone.
